f="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%C3%B9ng-Kh%E1%BA%AFc-Khoan/author-Pf4dpRXbHmTjs-pG65imRA">Phùng Khắc Khoan</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Quy%E1%BB%81n-%C4%90%E1%BB%A9c-D%C6%B0/Th%E1%BA%A5t-t%E1%BB%8Bch/poem-btkYyDh4Of4FceGNsTkb1w">Thất tịch - 七夕</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Quy%E1%BB%81n-%C4%90%E1%BB%A9c-D%C6%B0/author-_4d5nEBX-lxP-MgaFitnXg">Quyền Đức Dư</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/Th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-ho%C3%A0ng-t%C3%A2y-tu%E1%BA%A7n-nam-kinh-ca-k%E1%BB%B3-05/poem-FLHtHYPcAQxN_7jqfa_RPg">Thượng hoàng tây tuần nam kinh ca kỳ 05 - 上皇西巡南京歌其五</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/author-8WYDeeki5xZo8eD-k6Sk5A">Lý Bạch</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Nh%C3%A2n-T%C4%A9nh/Ti%C3%AAn-th%C3%A0nh-l%E1%BB%AF-kh%E1%BB%A9-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-GkJuGS5e4qcEId3qM-Y5bw">Tiên thành lữ khứ kỳ 2 - 仙城旅去其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Nh%C3%A2n-T%C4%A9nh/author-rBwuga23VinyqvRkAWczyA">Ngô Nhân Tĩnh</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
